"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "腾讯拟推出个人微信云存储付费服务，意味着微信聊天记录可以实现云端备份和恢复。 目前，微信仅支持迁移聊天记录到另一台设备以及备份聊天记录到电脑，如果设备丢失，未及时备份的数据将无法恢复。 据悉，该业务可能采用按年付费的模式，苹果用户或在 180 元 / 年左右，安卓用户或在 130 元 / 年左右。但该费用具体可以存储多大容量的数据尚未得到确定。 知情人士表示，当前该项目仍在最后推动中，具体细节未最终敲定。 截至发稿前，腾讯未给出明确回应。（中国日报）独家： 微信拟推出聊天记录付费云存储服务"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-91a0a1365a16572ba9e124f1df89700a_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "163 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/484674591"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIo6mOr53z05EFEAMaCDY5OTg3NDUwIO6rzIkGMIMBOIUOQA1yCTQ4NDY3NDU5MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1630801492.0537333", "card_id": "Q_331434969", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 338}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "极致收纳的家是什么样的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "收纳话题很一直火，假设一个家，将收纳做到极致，会是什么样的？是令人向往的样子吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c7ecfd0baa0edea5140827b5627ed18c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "146 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/331434969"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIo6mOr53z05EFEAMaCDM1OTI4OTk0IIbtx+gFMBM4lLgCQA5yCTMzMTQzNDk2OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1630801492.054048", "card_id": "Q_484706324", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 76}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2021 LPL 夏季赛冒泡赛 LNG 3:0 RA 晋级冒泡赛决赛，如何评价这场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "144 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/484706324"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Io6mOr53z05EFEAMaCDY5OTk0NTcyIKbmzIkGMAE4dkAPcgk0ODQ3MDYzMjR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_16308014